description:
Three friends who have come together out of nothing but a pure love of comics, three friends who moved hundreds of miles across the U.S. to follow their dreams, three friends who really didn't know what to put in the about section here so they figured if they kept writing three friends it would sound ominous and epic like a Hollywood film.

Along the way we met a great friend and final member of the group rounding us out to an awesome foursome and completing our epic journey.

But seriously folks, Atomic Rex is a group of writers/artists who have decided to unite together like a classic super hero team-up and put out some of the best comics with some of the best artists around, worthy of YOUR hard earned money.

Creator owned comic books will always come first and what we do most, but Atomic Rex was also developed in mind with an eye toward pen an paper role-playing games.

We're not established and we haven't written for one of the big two. But we're coming like a storm straight out of hell.

Atomic Rex Entertainment, the name says it all.
name: Atomic Rex Entertainment
